#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:8
msgid "## Independent"
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:10
msgid "* **Melendez Corp.**: Focuses on large cargo-oriented trade ships and heavy engines."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:11
msgid "* **Krain Industries**: Fabricator that makes the [Kestrel](ships/kestrel) and [Starbridge](ships/starbridge) and their assorted custom engines."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:12
msgid "* **Nexus Shipyards**: Makes a decent amount of ships for [the Empire](lore/factions/empire) and their civilian counterparts. Also makes engines and stealth armour."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:13
msgid "* **Aerosys**: Maker of the popular [Hyena](ships/hyena) interceptor."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:14
msgid "* **MilSpec**: Provides high-end cores and outfits. A favourite of bounty hunters."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:15
msgid "* **Unicorp**: Designs many accessible core outfits, and also launchers for the Caeser torpedoes, among others."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:16
msgid "* **Tricon**: Design high-end engines optimized for speed."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:17
msgid "* **Schafer & Kane Industries**: Manufacturer of heavy armour and cargo hulls."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:18
msgid "* **Imperial Red Star**: An organization dedicated to relief efforts that has also designed their own line of defensive armours."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:20
msgid "## Houses"
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:22
msgid "* **House Goddard**: Makes the [Goddard](ships/goddard) and is involved in the design of [House Dvaered](lore/factions/dvaered) ships."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:23
msgid "* **House Dvaered**: Works in tandem with House Goddard to develop the ships used by [House Dvaered](lore/factions/dvaered)."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:24
msgid "* **Sirius Systems**: Besides developing the ships for [House Sirius](lore/factions/sirius), also develops the [Schroedinger](ships/schroedinger) scout ship."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:25
msgid "* **Za'lek Fabricators**: Focuses on developing and making the ships flown by [House Za'lek](lore/factions/zalek)."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:26
msgid "* **Za'lek Robotics**: Produces [House Za'lek](lore/factions/zalek) drones."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:28
msgid "## Other"
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:29
msgid "* **Soromid**: Uses advanced genetic techniques to grow and train biological ships."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:30
msgid "* **Skull and Bones**: Known for stealing and developing variants of any ship they can get their hands on. Almost all the materials used are from dubious sources."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:32
msgid "* **Thurion Shipyards**: Produce ships with advanced interfaces for digital humans with minimal life support."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:35
msgid "* **Proteron**: Although they use an antiquated fabrication methods, they have refined them to the point they are extremely competitive with other ships."
msgstr ""

#: dat/naevpedia/lore/fabricators.md:38
msgid "* **Robosys**: Provides support and modifications for the Collective ships."
msgstr ""

